      <title>中国着眼加强市场监管以提振投资者信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/china-to-tighten-ipos-checks-on-listed-firms-to-boost-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国市场监管机构誓言收紧境内上市要求，并加强对上市公司的检查，这是为中国价值 9.2 万亿美元的股市注入信心的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/china-to-tighten-ipos-checks-on-listed-firms-to-boost-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 08:03:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
