      <title>IEA 将预测转向赤字，油价维持近四个月高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在国际能源署预测 2024 年供应短缺之后，油价维持在四个月高点附近——与之前的盈余预测相反——前提是OPEC+维持减产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 23:28:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>第一种治疗常见致命性肝病的药物获得美国批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/first-drug-to-treat-common-lethal-liver-disease-gets-us-nod</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Madrigal Pharmaceuticals Inc. 的药物 Rezdiffra 在美国首次获得批准，用于治疗一种可能致命的肝病，这种疾病影响了全球数百万人，在一些更大的竞争对手失败的领域取得了成功。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/first-drug-to-treat-common-lethal-liver-disease-gets-us-nod</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 19:53:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
